import Vue from 'vue'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import routers from './router.js'
import App from './App.vue'


Vue.config.productionTip = false

Vue.use(VueRouter)

const router = new VueRouter({
	mode:'history',
	routes:routers
})

new Vue({
	router,
  render: h => h(App)  
}).$mount('#app')
